In which British writers scold America on tradeIf you don't acknowledge the point of tariffs, how can you hope to criticize them? https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/in-which-british-writers-scold-america https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/in-which-british-writers-scold-americaNoah Smith Tue, 21 May 2024 10:07:17 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4eb2f2c9-9fa2-4a4b-b408-1ac24685909b_1174x548.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4eb2f2c9-9fa2-4a4b-b408-1ac24685909b_1174x548.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4eb2f2c9-9fa2-4a4b-b408-1ac24685909b_1174x548.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4eb2f2c9-9fa2-4a4b-b408-1ac24685909b_1174x548.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4eb2f2c9-9fa2-4a4b-b408-1ac24685909b_1174x548.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4eb2f2c9-9fa2-4a4b-b408-1ac24685909b_1174x548.jpeg" width="718" height="335.14821124361157" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4eb2f2c9-9fa2-4a4b-b408-1ac