stackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg" width="909" height="774" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:774,&quot;width&quot;:909,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:74749,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://networkcontagion.us/wp-content/uploads/A-Tik-Tok-ing-Timebomb_12.21.23.pdf">NCRI/罗格斯大学</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这主要是对美国人观点的无声审查。美国 TikTok 用户甚至没有意识到这种情况正在发生，因此这不太可能使他们的互联网体验变得更加负面。但随着时间的推移，TikTok 在美国宣扬<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2024/01/08/china-antisemitism-online-tool-west-gaza/">分裂态度</a>可能会影响人类舆论，使互联网变得比现在更加极端和喧闹。</p><p>当然，总有一些行为者试图在社交媒体上散布虚假信息、影响行动等等——企业、政党、利益集团等等。但中国和俄罗斯政府的资源比任何其他参与者都要好得多——他们有更多的资金、更多的人力和更多的技术致力于这项工作。大男孩们出来玩了，他们改变了我们的互联网，而且通常变得更糟。</p><h4>斜坡</h4><p>到目前为止，我提到的因素甚至在 ChatGPT 和 Midjourney 以及其他生成式 AI 应用程序的功能爆炸性增长并广泛使用之前就已经存在。现在，生产相当高质量的图像和文本的边际成本已接近于零。因此，人们正在使用生成式人工智能来填充社交媒体……的东西。</p><p>博客<a href="https://www.garbageday.email/">Garbage Day</a>是我最喜欢的跟踪互联网迷因的博客之一（另一个是<a href="https://www.infinitescroll.us/">Infinite Scroll</a> ），有<a href="https://www.garbageday.email/p/internet-looks-like-now">一篇关于这个……东西的好文章</a>。以下是 Facebook 上的一些图片，其中有孩子们驾驶由塑料瓶制成的汽车： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg" width="710" height="411.14355231143554" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/feb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:476,&quot;width&quot;:822,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:710,&quot;bytes&quot;:156564,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">来源：<a href="https://www.garbageday.email/">垃圾日</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>马克斯·迈耶 (Max Meyer) 一直在社交媒体烹饪视频中钻研，这些视频展示了人工智能制作的<a href="https://twitter.com/mualphaxi/status/1787658007028924754">无意义食谱</a>，并配有人工智能旁白。<a href="https://twitter.com/FacebookAIslop">从那以后事情只会变得更奇怪</a>。</p><p>孩子们驾驶塑料瓶制成的汽车的图像有何意义？废话食谱有什么意义？答案是：<em>不一定有什么意义</em>。由于生产这些东西的边际成本基本上为零，并且至少有一些非零的机会，这些随机的东西中的任何一个都会流行并成为模因并让人们订阅频道并赚取一些广告收入，这是有道理的尽可能多地向世界发送垃圾邮件。</p><p>事实上，“Slop”正在迅速成为人工智能生成的平庸至糟糕内容的标准术语： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg" width="596" height="562.7657992565056" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:762,&quot;width&quot;:807,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:596,&quot;bytes&quot;:168656,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc1cf8cd8-e6a3-468c-8006-bb32681a3daa_807x762.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>从任何单一污水生成器的角度来看，生成越来越多的污水可能是一个经济上合理的主张。但它产生了负外部性，即其他人的互联网体验变得越来越无聊，有些令人讨厌的废话。未来，问题可能会变得更加严重；人工智能甚至可能会在人工智能生成的斜坡上<a href="https://www.popularmechanics.com/technology/a44675279/ai-content-model-collapse/">训练自己</a>，将整个互联网变成一个递归的斜坡乌洛波洛斯。 “<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/danidiplacido/2024/01/16/the-dead-internet-theory-explained/">死亡互联网理论</a>”目前是一个愚蠢有趣的阴谋论，但它可能在不远的将来成为现实。</p><h4>谎言之神进入谎言之网</h4><p>已故的<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/go-read-some-vernor-vinge">弗诺·文奇（Vernor Vinge）</a>是我一直以来最喜欢的科幻小说作家之一，他写了一个系列，其中银河互联网被称为<a href="https://reactormag.com/the-net-of-a-million-lies-vernor-vinges-a-fire-upon-the-deep/">“百万谎言之网”</a> （显然是在取笑他自己在新闻组上的经历）。这与一句俗话“谎言可以走遍半个地球，真相才得以出现”有关——因为制造错误信息的边际成本远小于反驳错误信息的边际成本，这是一个自由、非中介的市场的想法往往会传播很多谎言。大量研究表明，错误信息<a href="https://news.mit.edu/2018/study-twitter-false-news-travels-faster-true-stories-0308">在社交媒体上的传播速度实际上比真实信息更快</a>。</p><p>这就是为什么人类传统上依赖信息看门人——报纸编辑、电视主播等——来防止我们成为全职事实核查者。社交媒体上很少有这样的看门人，2016 年大选后，关于我们是否需要某种企业编辑控制以减少社交媒体上传播的错误信息量，存在着一场巨大的（且持续的）辩论。</p><p>我不会在这里重述这场争论，但我会说生成式人工智能绝对会加剧这个问题。现在，制作某人声音的深度伪造品几乎是轻而易举的事，经过人工智能处理的图像也很容易，而且深度伪造视频也正在实现这一目标。这不是未来的推测问题——它现在正在发生。</p><p>人工智能造假可<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/02/04/asia/deepfake-cfo-scam-hong-kong-intl-hnk/index.html">用于诈骗</a>：</p><blockquote><p> A finance worker at a multinational firm was tricked into paying out $25 million to fraudsters using deepfake technology to pose as the company&#39;s chief financial officer in a video conference call, according to Hong Kong police.</p><p> The elaborate scam saw the worker duped into attending a video call with what he thought were several other members of staff, but all of whom were in fact deepfake recreations, Hong Kong police said at a briefing on Friday.</p></blockquote><p> AI fakery can be used <a href="https://www.thebaltimorebanner.com/education/k-12-schools/eric-eiswert-ai-audio-baltimore-county-YBJNJAS6OZEE5OQVF5LFOFYN6M/">for personal revenge</a> :</p><blockquote><p> Baltimore County Police arrested<strong> </strong>Pikesville High School&#39;s former athletic director Thursday morning and charged him with crimes related to the alleged use of artificial intelligence to impersonate Principal Eric Eiswert, leading the public to believe Eiswert made <a href="https://www.thebaltimorebanner.com/education/k-12-schools/pikesville-high-principal-eric-eiswert-NT7K7N4K6RDEJNL5Z7ULTEG7VY/">racist and antisemitic comments</a> behind closed doors…Darien was charged with disrupting school activities after investigators determined he faked Eiswert&#39;s voice and circulated the audio on social media in January[.]</p></blockquote><p> AI fakery can be used <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2024/02/01/politics/election-deepfake-threats-invs/index.html">for politics</a> :</p><blockquote><p> Days before a pivotal election in Slovakia to determine who would lead the country, a damning audio recording spread online in which one of the top candidates seemingly boasted about how he&#39;d rigged the election…The recordings immediately went viral on social media, and the candidate, who is pro-NATO and aligned with Western interests, was defeated in September by an opponent who supported closer ties to Moscow and Russian President Vladimir Putin.</p><p> While the number of votes swayed by the leaked audio remains uncertain, two things are now abundantly clear: The recordings were fake, created using artificial intelligence; and US officials see the episode in Europe as a frightening harbinger of the sort of interference the United States will likely experience during the 2024 presidential election.</p></blockquote><p> AI fakery can even be used <a href="https://petapixel.com/2024/04/15/netflix-accused-of-using-ai-photos-in-true-crime-documentary/">for corporate media content</a> :</p><blockquote><p> Netflix has been accused of using AI-manipulated images in a new true crime documentary <em>What Jennifer Did</em> …The documentary revolves around Jennifer Pan who was convicted of a kill-for-hire attack on her parents. Around 28 minutes into the documentary, Pan&#39;s high school friend Nam Nguyen is described as a “bubbly, happy, confident, and very genuine” person. His words are accompanied by a series of relevant photos…But upon closer inspection of the images, there are signs of manipulation; one image in particular showing Pan flashing peace signs with both arms appears blatantly manipulated offering evidence that at least some of the image was AI-generated.</p></blockquote><p> It&#39;s not yet clear how deepfakes can be controlled. States are <a href="https://www.understandingai.org/p/states-are-racing-ahead-of-congress">rushing to roll out regulations</a> designed to limit deepfakes, but whether it&#39;ll even remain technologically possible to detect a deepfake as the technology improves is uncertain. One possible future equilibrium is that people just learn not to trust anything they see or hear on the public internet (or on an unverified phone call, text, or email).</p><p> Perhaps we&#39;ve finally perfected the Net of Lies by creating a God of Lies to rule over it.</p><p> So the internet as we know it — social media sites and the Web — is becoming a generally worse place to hang out. Wading through oceans of advertisements, algorithmic randomness antisemitic Russian bots, Tiktok-poisoned shouters, AI slop, and deepfakes is just not a fun way to spend anyone&#39;s precious limited lifetime.</p><p> Better, perhaps, to simply withdraw from the public internet — to spend one&#39;s time chatting directly with friends and in small groups, having fun offline, and maybe watching TV or reading a book or a Substack. That sort of human interaction worked fine before the internet, and it will probably work just fine today. Which is why despite the fact that all of the trends I mentioned are negative, I&#39;m optimistic about the future of our digital communications and our media diet. Maybe someday historians will look back on the era when we lived our lives on social networking sites as a brief anomaly. </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-death-again-of-the-internet-as?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-death-again-of-the-internet-as?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p></p><p></p>; 
