ic%2Fimages%2F6c1dd462-2041-4a8f-80f7-6cadf0d85e51_1600x906.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6c1dd462-2041-4a8f-80f7-6cadf0d85e51_1600x906.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6c1dd462-2041-4a8f-80f7-6cadf0d85e51_1600x906.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：Claus Aasholm、SemiBizIntel、自己的研究</figcaption></figure></div><p>中芯国际的目标是进入更先进的节点，但目前还很困难。中芯国际正在平衡使用他们仍然可以使用的较旧的西方设备和他们自己的中国本土生态系统，这些生态系统大多只是从相同的西方设备复制而来。 And even if they did have access to the best western equipment, they would not have the know-how to make it work for them. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png" width="525" height="427" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:427,&quot;width&quot;:525,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27f4f5b0-367c-4b96-8425-8f9f3aea7a6c_525x427.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> Source: IC Insights, 2022</figcaption></figure></div><p>与此同时，它们确实正在淹没成熟的节点市场。虽然个别成熟节点芯片的利润可能较低，但它维持了业务并实现了创建阻塞点的战略目标。</p><p>这种刻意的“淹没”，你可以在习近平的讲话《关于我国经济社会中长期发展战略的重大问题》中看到，需要认真对待。</p><h4> <strong>The US Response Strategy so far: The CHIPS Act</strong></h4><p> 《CHIPS 法案》对于让美国在国内芯片生产方面走上正确的道路至关重要。我们不应该完全忽视低节点芯片。考虑到失去台积电的真实风险，它们非常关键。然而，该法案并没有充分解决中国激进战略所需的平衡问题。</p><p>回到军事供应链，我们系统中使用的芯片估计有 20-40% 来自中国。军用硬件中的组件数量庞大，因此验证每个芯片（例如通用微控制器）的来源是不切实际的。这是令人担忧的，特别是因为其中一些芯片可能来自与中国军方有联系的公司，从而带来侧通道和加密攻击的风险。</p><p> CHIPS 法案通过向国内外公司提供贷款、赠款和补贴来刺激制造业，以扩大其在美国的制造能力。尽管最初怀疑 NIST 或国会部能否完成任何工作，但该计划似乎正在发挥作用。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png" width="1456" height="801" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/bb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:801,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbb3d3add-677b-4957-abe4-6f2836947b5f_1600x880.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> Source: McKinsey, The CHIPS and Science Act: Here&#39;s what&#39;s in it, 2022 </figcaption></figure></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png" width="1456" height="1325" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1325,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27b9139b-6ac5-4816-b119-85b06e8144e1_1600x1456.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://clausaasholm.substack.com/">克劳斯·阿肖姆</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>缺少一件事：成熟的节点。 Currently, only $2b has been given out in grants for mature nodes and somewhere between $8-$10b is earmarked for it eventually. Most of the money will go into leading edge chips.</p><p>不想过于愤世嫉俗，但英特尔和 GlobalFoundries 确实对该法案的内容做出了贡献，这一事实应该让这一结果毫不奇怪。在没有令人难以置信的容量/完全折旧设备的设施中，并且如果设施是新的则更没有意义，很难使成熟节点的经济性发挥作用。</p><p>我完全支持在设计经济政策方面进行公私合作，有人可能会认为，在美国产能已经启动并运行时进行友好外包或推动成熟节点可能是更好的策略。如果中国人不是故意这么做的话，这些论点就会更有道理。我们需要更加积极主动地做出有效反应。</p><h4> <strong>The Solution: Offensive and Defensive</strong></h4><p>我们可以从防守和进攻两个方面来解决这个问题。我建议同时进行两者。</p><p>前两个是赌注。我将其称为防御行为。</p><ol><li><p>我们需要投入更多的资金来开发成熟的节点芯片。</p></li><li><p>我们需要更加积极地监控军用芯片的供应链。</p></li></ol><p>后两者可能更痛苦。我称它们为进攻性行为。</p><ol start="3"><li><p>我们需要对所有节点规模的中国芯片实施更全面的关税制度。</p></li><li><p> We have sanctioned equipment for leading edge nodes, but we need to push this further, even into software tools like Cadence and Synopsys.</p></li></ol><p>我认为前两个单独存在是不够的，因为在价格竞争中，我们永远不会获胜，特别是当我们正在提高国内产量或解决芯片友好支持问题时。</p><p> The third is something that is not exactly pretty, but they will give our domestic chip industry price pressure reprieve to ramp up.不仅如此，这还将给中芯国际带来财务压力。</p><p>第四种是最具攻击性的，肯定会不受欢迎。应用材料公司约45%的收入来自中国。将其从该市场切断将是极其痛苦的，我们将不得不补偿他们的损失。批评者会说“如果我们切断它们，他们最终会建立自己的国内竞争对手”，这是事实，但是，就像关税一样，它是一个生硬的工具，可以减缓中国的步伐，让我们提高国内产能。</p><p>芯片只是过去二十年来我们与中国进行的一场更大规模的经济和地缘政治斗争的一个方面。 We&#39;ve been caught on a backfooting, out of naivete or lack of resolve, but at least on chips, we must reverse course. </p>